{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["Preheat oven to 160°C. Grease and line sides and base of a cake tin (Ø 23 cm) with baking paper.","Place beetroot in mixing bowl and grate <b>4 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides and lid of mixing bowl with spatula then grate again <b>4 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place chocolate in mixing bowl and grate <b>8 sec\/speed 8<b> then melt <b>3 min\/50°C\/speed 4<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then melt again <b>1 min\/50°C\/speed 4<b>.","Add sugar, flour, almonds, oil, bicarbonate of soda, baking powder and vanilla extract then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add eggs and reserved grated beetroot then mix <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Transfer to prepared tin. Bake for 55-60 minutes (160°C) until a skewer inserted in centre comes out clean. Leave to cool in tin. Meanwhile, clean mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Icing","content":["Once cake is cool, remove from tin. Place vanilla sugar in mixing bowl and grind <b>30 sec\/speed 10<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula.","Add cream cheese then mix <b>10 sec\/speed 4<b>. Spread icing over top of cake and serve garnished with roughly chopped chocolate."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Sponge","content":["100 g sunflower oil, plus extra for greasing","250 g beetroot, raw, peeled, cut in pieces (see tip)","250 g dark chocolate, small pieces or callets","200 g light muscovado sugar","100 g self-raising flour","50 g ground almonds","½ tsp bicarbonate of soda","½ tsp baking powder","1 tsp vanilla extract","2 large eggs"]},{"title":"Icing","content":["80 g vanilla sugar","200 g cream cheese","50 g dark chocolate, roughly chopped, for garnish"]}],"id":"r130862","imageLink":"https:\/\/2.bp.blogspot.com\/-mzeeyYtSLXE\/XZWqNR-LAcI\/AAAAAAAAfUk\/Frqfg4gM4JwxmZa3QjjMJPYFc2kuUKQ3QCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_FT3Iy8Pmj-0c_T0v.png","title":"Chocolate Beetroot Cake","publishedAt":"2017-03-27T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"7.5 g","fat":"35.9 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"48.9 g","calories":"2299 kJ \/ 549 kcal"},"usefulItems":"spring form tin (Ø 23 cm), baking paper, skewer, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Use rubber gloves when peeling beetroot to protect hands from staining."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","2h 20m","10 slices"]}